data.description: This recently updated MOVE IN READY home in prime location features a spacious main living area, 3 main level bedrooms, 3 full baths and a finished basement to go along with loads of upgrades. Highlights include new cabinets, countertops, appliances & tile backsplash in the tastefully remodeled kitchen, gorgeous laminate flooring throughout the main living area, and a new (2021) relaxing back deck that overlooks the large level backyard. The finished basement offers a cozy stone wood-burning fireplace in the rec room, a full bathroom, and a home office (possible 4th bedroom). Located just minutes from all major points in West Knoxville including area schools (Bluegrass, West Valley and Bearden) and Ft. Loudon Lake.
